Feature: HeroQuest
  As a logged in user, I should be able to initiate a quest that I am within range of
  As a logged in user, I should be able to initiate a chapter of a quest that I have started
  # do you need to be within range for each chapter start, or just for picking up the initial quest? Can you go somewhere else and keep going with the quest?
  AS a logged in user, I should be able to view the results of a quest chapter I have completed
  As a logged in user, I should be able to claim the reward for a quest I have completed

  Scenario: A user starts a new quest and initiates a chapter

  Scenario: A user views the results of a chapter

  Scenario: A user claims a quest reward